<template>
    <section class="container">
        <v-calendar is-expanded :attributes='attrs'/>
    </section>
    
</template>

<style scoped>

</style>

<script>
export default  {
    data() {
    return {
        attrs: [
      {
        key: 'today',
        highlight: {
          color: 'purple',
          fillMode: 'solid',
          contentClass: 'italic',
        },
        dates: new Date(year, month, 12),
      },
      {
        highlight: {
          color: 'purple',
          fillMode: 'light',
        },
        dates: new Date(year, month, 13),
      },
      {
        highlight: {
          color: 'purple',
          fillMode: 'outline',
        },
        dates: new Date(year, month, 14),
      },
    ],
    };
  },
}
</script>
